<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<strong>Maggie:</strong> Hey! Who're you calling a shark?</p>
<p><strong>Russell:</strong> Not sure, but I heard him call himself a shark a minute ago&#8230;</p>
<p><strong>Segal:</strong> <em>[cracks knuckles]</em></p>
<p><strong>Adrian:</strong> Guys? Stay back! Guys, please! Hey! No!</p>
<p><em>[Everyone proceeds to beat Adrian senseless until everything just fucking explodes. The end.]</em></p>
</blockquote>
